{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">My name is Kuri Rose, and I am not a weapon.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Their world is slowly disappearing... one girl stands in defiance of the eternal void.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784150/extras/About1.png?t=1736498103\" />The Last Rose is an apocalypse adventure visual novel about Kuri Rose, friend to some, sister to another, weapon to everyone else. After her untimely death, she finds herself stuck in the middle of an apocalypse led by her ex-boyfriend's brother.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on an adventure that spans across time alongside a large cast of interesting and varied characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At the end of the world, will you be able to defy the inevitable?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784150/extras/features1.png?t=1736498103\" />\ud83c\udf39 <strong>A Sprawling Story</strong>: The Last Rose spans over 100,000 words long. Sink your teeth into this hearty tale of the world's end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf39 <strong>Multiple Endings</strong>: Play through three distinct routes, one of which features a romantic relationship, while the others tell stories of family, friends, and people once loved.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf39 <strong>Gorgeous Original Art</strong>: Lose yourself in the striking visuals that bring the story to life by the fantastic Miyukiko and\u00a0ombobon.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784150/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736498103","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store